The SNAP Graph takes all Sentinel-2 L2A optical iamgery:
- Subsets it to a bounding box.
- Selects all bands and the SCL bands
- Resamples all bands to B2 (10m)
- Create a band usign the SCL 
- Exports as a GEOtiff

The code does the following
1 - Clips all data to the AOI
2 - Masks clouds using the SCL band. return to 12 bands
3 - Selects bands and calcualtes indicies
4 - Runs unsupervised classification